snippet.title: Rake PC Game Review
snippet.description:
Buy the game here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/386880/
Join the Gggmanlives Steam Group: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/gggmanlives
Reddit Fanpage: http://www.reddit.com/r/Gggmanlives/

Do ghosts exist? What about Bigfoot, Chupacabras, Rake or Skinwalkers? And how will we ever know? You play as Gordon Davis, a scientist,a traveller and an explorer of unknown creatures and unusual events.
